{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1849064, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2614, "w": 1649}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1623640150, "type": "image", "url": "5l/5lnkixyi3fpzz2viegu5tg5ylgqizkxu.jpeg"}, {"cid": 1849083, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "搜了下，有诉讼时效", "timestamp": 1623640274, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849092, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是的 为了使法律关系尽快确定 有诉讼时效的规定 世界上大部分国家都有类似规定的", "timestamp": 1623640329, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849095, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有，这个在我国叫诉讼时效，一般诉讼时效是3年，最长不超过20年，但是我国不区分民事商事，并且我国诉讼时效的中断也挺方便的，只要你催债了，不用诉讼，就中断", "timestamp": 1623640370, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849096, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849092, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 那我拖五年就不用还钱了，岂不美哉", "timestamp": 1623640373, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849106, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849095, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 哦哦，只要催一次就不会要不回来了？", "timestamp": 1623640449, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849116, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849064, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 诉讼时效有中断的制度，就是说，债主要五年一直没找你要钱，你才不用还，如果债主催讨了，就不发生诉讼时效效力，不过保证期间倒是硬拖，把6个月拖过了不去起诉，就真逃过了。。。。。", "timestamp": 1623640519, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849127, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 还有一个问题，既然法官懂法，那他怎么不直接驳回原告的要求呢。电视剧里这个老头子本来都要输了，要不是有人来帮他就得乖乖掏钱，法官坐在上面却无动于衷。", "timestamp": 1623640606, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849127, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 尊重当事人意思，当事人自己乐意还钱没人管它", "timestamp": 1623640739, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849147, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849127, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为诉讼时效必须由当事人主张，法官主动驳回是违法的。", "timestamp": 1623640795, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849152, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849127, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 而且诉讼时效的存在是价值取舍问题，毕竟欠债还钱天经地义，几年不催就不用还这个事本身也不太合理，所以，没必要法官主动适用", "timestamp": 1623640810, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849154, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849127, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 本来这就对债权人不友好，如果法官还能主动用，就太不友好了", "timestamp": 1623640828, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849159, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849127, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在民法最发达的德国，诉讼时效可是三十年哦", "timestamp": 1623640875, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849160, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849127, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 在我国，援引诉讼时效是一种抗辩权，是法官不能够主动适用，甚至不能告知一方当事人其有这个权利，法官主动适用的抗辩只有合同无效或诉讼上的抗辩等少数几项。", "timestamp": 1623640884, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849166, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849159, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 谢谢Carol Dave Eve！", "timestamp": 1623640930, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849169, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849166, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 原来洞里有这么多法学院的大佬hh感觉法律好神奇，有各种奇妙的玩法", "timestamp": 1623640962, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849176, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849166, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以以后遇到事，记得出高价请一个清华法学院毕业的律师，给我们一口饭吃x", "timestamp": 1623641031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849184, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849160, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这就是法官中立原则，即使我知道你要输了，但是我是中立的裁判者，我也不会告诉你你要输了。不过顺便一提，我国没有罚则，也就是说就算法官违反中立义务进行释明或主动援引，也没有啥后果，我还见过讨要加班费时法官直接对劳动者说你能多要一点。。。。。至于哪种体制更好，就看Dz自己的价值判断了", "timestamp": 1623641091, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849199, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849176, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 哈哈哈哈有机会一定", "timestamp": 1623641207, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849201, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849176, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 不过自己学一点民法是不是比较省钱（", "timestamp": 1623641226, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1849210, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1849184, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 嗯嗯，谢谢Carol", "timestamp": 1623641302, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1850854, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这是成宝拉吗！", "timestamp": 1623657867, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1850929, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 362769, "reply_to": 1850854, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 是哎", "timestamp": 1623658631, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 362769, "reply": 23, "tag": null, "text": "昨天受洞里诱惑刷了一部韩剧，确实如dz所说是一部普法剧hh\n所以我们国家也有这么神奇的制度吗，欠债之后不用还钱？", "timestamp": 1623640139, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1623658630, "url": "", "vote": {}}}